<i>adverb</i>: 무한히 [무한히], 마냥 [마냥], 끝없이 [끄덥씨] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>무한히 [무한히]</dt><br>
<dd>infinitely; limitlessly; endlessly</dd><br>
<dd>수나 양, 크기, 공간이나 시간의 끝이나 제한이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>With no end or limit of number, amount, size, space or time.</dd><br>
<dt>마냥 [마냥]</dt><br>
<dd>1. infinitely</dd><br>
<dd>언제까지나 계속하여.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuously without end.</dd><br>
<dd>2. to the full</dd><br>
<dd>부족함이 없이 실컷.</dd><br>
<dd>As much as one likes, without feeling the lack of something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. so much</dd><br>
<dd>보통 이상으로 몹시.</dd><br>
<dd>To the extent of being more than the average.</dd><br>
<dt>끝없이 [끄덥씨]</dt><br>
<dd>endlessly; infinitely</dd><br>
<dd>끝이 없거나 제한이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without end or limit.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>